📸 Demo (Before & After)
Normal State	Drowsy Detected
🚨 Alert System (How It Works)
🔹 Sound Alert – Pygame triggers an alarm sound when drowsiness is detected.
🔹 Email Alert – Sends an alert email to a caretaker.
🔹 SMS Alert – Sends a text message to a registered phone number.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Python 🐍
OpenCV (for face & eye tracking)
DLib (for landmark detection)
Pygame (for sound alerts)
Twilio & SMTP (for SMS/Email alerts)
📌 Future Enhancements
🚀 Mobile App Integration – Sync with a mobile app for real-time notifications
🎯 Better AI Accuracy – Improve detection using deep learning models
🌐 Cloud Alerts – Send alerts via a cloud service

